     <h2>Enclosure: Invoice from Joseph Gardoqui &amp; Sons to John Adams</h2>
     
     <div class="docbody">
      <div class="opener">
       <table class="salutationBlock">
        <tr>
		<td class="salutationRight">Bilbao 31st. Jany 1780<a class="ptr" href="#PJA08d229n1" id="PJA08d229n1-ptr">1</a></td>
	      </tr>
      </table>
      </div>
      <p>Invoice of Sundries shippd per the Phinix James Babson master for Newburyport on Account of the Honble. John Adams Esq.</p>
